OL,3,C'The Fudge Man' - making a difference
OL,4,Cone box at a time
OL,6,FBy day he works in a dental surgery.
OL,7,FBut ironically, in his spare time,
OL,8,FPaul Lees has raised thousands of
OL,9,Fpounds for charity by making fudge in
OL,10,Fhis kitchen.
OL,12,FIt's led him to being among the
OL,13,Fnominees for ITV Meridian's Pride of
OL,14,FBritain Regional Fundraiser of the
OL,15,FYear Award.
OL,17,FPaul, from Gosport, started One Box of
OL,18,FFudge in November 2022, when he was
OL,19,Frecovering from an injury that had
OL,20,Fleft him housebound.
