OL,3,C'The Fudge Man' - making a difference
OL,4,Cone box at a time
OL,6,FHe made batches as Christmas presents
OL,7,Ffor family when he couldn't get out
OL,8,Fshopping -and was then encouraged to
OL,9,Fcarry on making the confectionary by
OL,10,Ffamily and friends.
OL,12,FSince then, Paul has dedicated all of
OL,13,Fhis free time to making fudge and has
OL,14,Fsold over 3000 boxes, donating every
OL,15,Fpenny of profit to local charities.
