OL,3,C'The Fudge Man' - making a difference
OL,4,Cone box at a time
OL,6,FHe makes around 20 flamboyant flavours
OL,7,Fincluding his favourite - Rum and
OL,8,FRaisin - and an array of chocolate
OL,9,Ffudges. His latest creation is a
OL,10,Fpumpkin spiced latte fudge for
OL,11,FHalloween.
OL,13,FPaul, who works as a dental practice
OL,14,Fmanager in Fareham, has been given the
OL,15,Fnickname 'The Fudge Man' - and admits
OL,16,Fthat it's a bit of a joke that he
OL,17,Fworks in a dental surgery.
