OL,3,C'The Fudge Man' - making a difference
OL,4,Cone box at a time
OL,6,F"It is totally ironic." he laughs.
OL,7,F"It's not bad for your teeth if you
OL,8,Fhave it with a meal. So as a qualified
OL,9,Fdental nurse, I can tell you you're
OL,10,Fallowed.
OL,12,F"I can only blame the customers - if
OL,13,Fpeople buy it, I'll be making
OL,14,Fit....and it's for a good cause."
OL,16,FPaul hand delivers the sweet treats -
OL,17,Fin the Gosport and Fareham area four
OL,18,Fnights a week.
