OL,4,Cone box at a time
OL,6,FDonations have gone to more than 40
OL,7,Flocal charities including Fareham and
OL,8,FGosport Basics Bank and Y Services
OL,9,FLGBTQ+, plus local schools and youth
OL,10,Fgroups.
OL,12,FPaul said: "It's through One Box of
OL,13,FFudge where I've really connected with
OL,14,Fthe community and I've realized just
OL,15,Fhow many amazing people are doing
OL,16,Famazing things."
