OL,4,Cone box at a time
OL,6,FSometimes demand has been so high that
OL,7,FPaul has had to be up at the crack of
OL,8,Fdawn to cope with orders. "Sometimes I
OL,9,Fstart making fudge five in the morning
OL,10,Fand I've still been stirring till ten
OL,11,Fat night. Christmas is mega-popular."
OL,13,FHe says the secret of a good fudge is
OL,14,Fto get it to exactly the right
OL,15,Ftemperature - 116 degrees - and
OL,16,Fafterwards keep stirring it for
OL,17,Fexactly six minutes.
