OL,3,C'The Fudge Man' - making a difference
OL,4,Cone box at a time
OL,6,F"I'm unbelievably proud of how much
OL,7,Fmoney I've raised," he said. "There's
OL,8,Fbeen donations that I've literally
OL,9,Fbeen in tears about. It's very close
OL,10,Fto my heart.
OL,12,F"I'm proud it's still going, it's all
OL,13,Fvery unexpected but it's down to my
OL,14,Fcustomers."
OL,16,F"My first target was #3,000, which I
OL,17,Fnever thought I'd reach and now here
OL,18,Fwe are."
OL,20,FPaul has now set his next fundraising
OL,21,Ftarget at #25,000.
